PageWellTower partner Epoch Senior Living contact form

Requesterpool@jpdev.pro

Score2581
Tested byTestaro, procedure ts24
Scored byTestilo, procedure tsp24
Digested byTestilo, procedure tdp24

Introduction

This is a digest of results from a battery of accessibility Tests.

The battery includes 1353 automated accessibility tests drawn from ten different packages: Alfa, Axe, Continuum, Equal Access, HTML CodeSniffer, Nu Html Checker, QualWeb, Tenon, Testaro, and WAVE.

These tests were run on the web page named above and gave the page a score of 2581, where 0 would be perfect.

Issue summary

Special issues

log: Score 186. This is based on the amount of browser error logging and miscellaneous logging during the tests.

solos: Score 2. This is based on issues reported by unclassified tests. Details are in the report.

Classified issues

Issue duplicateID

WCAG: 4.1.1

Score: 560

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package alfa, test r3, score 336 (Element id attribute value is not unique)
  • Package axe, test duplicate-id, score 42 (id attribute value is not unique)
  • Package continuum, test 94, score 336 (Element contains an id attribute set to a value that is not unique in the DOM)
  • Package htmlcs, test e:AAA.4_1_1.F77, score 168 (Duplicate id attribute value)
  • Package ibm, test RPT_Elem_UniqueId, score 8 (Element id attribute value is not unique within the document)

Issue linkForcesNewWindow

WCAG: 3.2.5

Score: 275

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package tenon, test 218, score 273 (Link opens in a new window without user control)

Issue imageMapAreaNoText

WCAG: 1.1.1

Score: 192

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package htmlcs, test e:AAA.1_1_1.H24, score 68 (Area element in an image map has no alt attribute)
  • Package ibm, test WCAG20_Area_HasAlt, score 68 (Area element in an image map has no text alternative)
  • Package ibm, test HAAC_Img_UsemapAlt, score 68 (Image map or child area has no text alternative)
  • Package wave, test e:alt_area_missing, score 68 (Image map area has no alternative text)
